{"tid":1278398,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"業界分析：相比3A大作 更薄、更小的主機才是主導硬件銷量的重要因素","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T13:36:48.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfeb93be04ad5fcf25986ecd6d64f7a1a19a5fc","tid":1278398,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2371436849793489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2371436849793489&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=c584a984\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2371436849793489</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBvZTtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBvZTtJ.png&h=8edb4ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【業界】業界分析：相比3A大作 主機精簡化才是主導硬件銷量重要因素</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  7月1日，日本遊戲界分析專家安田秀樹發表了題為《主機精簡化成主導硬件銷量趨勢的重要因素》的文章，<strong><ins>指出了相比3A大作會極大帶動主機銷量的通常看法，實際上主機精簡化才是主導硬件銷量重要因素</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n  安田秀樹指出，根據多年各大遊戲主機的發售趨勢來看，AAA大作已經不是決定主機普及的根本性因素，根據整體主流主機的銷量趨勢增長表來看，<strong><ins>舉例來說，任天堂的改版DSLite發售時，DS的整體銷量趨勢發生了陡升</ins></strong>，而通常這種情況只會發生在年末商戰大促銷時期；另一方面，<strong><ins>索尼系的PSP在精簡版PSP2000推出時同樣發生銷量陡升現象</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n  雖然大多數玩家們都認為3A大作是決定主機銷量的根本性因素，不過<strong><ins>任天堂、索尼等老廠或許早已經達成了&ldquo;更加薄、更加小的主機&rdquo;才是重新拉動遊戲主機銷量的根本鑰匙的共識</ins></strong>，至少在新主機問世之前。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8c9wfp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8c9wfp.png&h=e6705ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CpG6OK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CpG6OK.png&h=cc1906f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brL7hVq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrL7hVq.png&h=08827715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>Sony PS5</ins></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[太貴，不了?] 分析師：以PS5的配置，它售價可能會在500美元（約合港幣3900元）或再高一點</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1272728/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1272728/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《華爾街日報》:Sony PS5主要強化與大型發行商之間的關係 忽略小型工作室的獨立遊戲</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1270528/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1270528/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[PS5] SomaSim聯合創始人表示 PS5 採用新技術，光線反射將隨處可見</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1257835/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1257835/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>SIE總裁Jim Ryan發表更多關於PS5的信息︰SSD將成為標配、支持4K分辨率下的120Hz</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1187165/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1187165/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>Nintendo Switch</ins></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[Switch]《華爾街日報》報導:Nintendo正在醞釀Lite和Pro版本兩款Switch主機 19年聖誕上線</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1261971/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1261971/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>距離任天堂 Switch Mini 的推出已經不遠了!? 從旺宏電子收到的訂單中透露端倪？</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1244309/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1244309/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e0bd328c0e4a881f19bf60e94b7893474fc85c49","tid":1278398,"uid":173852,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n無塞爾達 pkm搵撚買你switch咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ab25239777e9a2ce5f4fe4ed67075bebeffae2","tid":1278398,"uid":46389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"邊有人對住部機打J<br />\n要J都J game啦下話"},{"pid":"7f6a86d6011c7b0074fd8be94fd7f2765d35033a","tid":1278398,"uid":750